<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - เกมตอบคำถามสหกรณ์</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap');
    
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #c8e6c9 50%, #a5d6a7 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: 'Sarabun', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    }
    .auth-card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.15);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    }
    .auth-title {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43a047 0%, #66bb6a 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .form-control {
      border: 2px solid #a5d6a7;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .form-control:focus {
      border-color: #43a047;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(67, 160, 71, 0.1);
      background: white;
    }
    .form-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2e7d32;
    }
    .btn-login {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43a047 0%, #66bb6a 100%);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 40px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(67, 160, 71, 0.3);
    }
    .btn-login:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(67, 160, 71, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #388e3c 0%, #4caf50 100%);
    }
    .fade-in {
      animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center min-vh-100">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-5">
        <div class="card auth-card p-4 fade-in">
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <i class="bi bi-shield-lock display-3 mb-3" style="color: #43a047;"></i>
              <h1 class="auth-title mb-3">เข้าสู่ระบบ Admin</h1>
              <p class="text-muted">จัดการคำถาม รหัสเกม และสถิติของเกม</p>
            </div>

            <form method="POST" action="/coopgame/admin/login">
              <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="username" class="form-label">
                  <i class="bi bi-person-fill"></i> ชื่อผู้ใช้
                </label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="username"
                  name="username"
                  class="form-control"
                  value="<%= username || '' %>"
                  placeholder="admin"
                  autocomplete="username"
                  required
                >
              </div>

              <div class="mb-4">
                <label for="password" class="form-label">
                  <i class="bi bi-key-fill"></i> รหัสผ่าน
                </label>
                <input
                  type="password"
                  id="password"
                  name="password"
                  class="form-control"
                  placeholder="••••••••"
                  autocomplete="current-password"
                  required
                >
              </div>

              <div class="d-grid mb-3">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-login text-white">
                  <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right"></i> เข้าสู่ระบบ
                </button>
              </div>
            </form>

            <% if (error) { %>
              <div class="alert mt-3" style="background: #ffebee; color: #c62828; border: 1px solid #ffcdd2;" role="alert">
                <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill me-2" style="color: #e53935;"></i>
                <%= error %>
              </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="text-center mt-3">
              <small class="text-muted">
                <i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> หากยังไม่ได้ตั้งค่า `ADMIN_USERNAME` และ `ADMIN_PASSWORD` จะใช้ค่าดีฟอลต์จากระบบ
              </small>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
